snippet.title: Destroy Porn Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the launch trailer for our new game Destroy the Porn. The game is a cross between Metroid and Super Meat Boy. It's a fun little 10 minute platformer, and you should check it out at: http://www.drunkdevs.com/games/2013/2/10/destroy-the-porn.html

music for the video was provided by:
Dan Johansen
http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/513002

Sandwich95
http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/407858

If you enjoy the game you can follow us on twitter at
@DrunkDevs
like us on facebook
http://www.facebook.com/DrunkDevs
and be sure to check out our site:
http://www.drunkdevs.com
